articles.title: Made In China Shaanxi Y-8 Aircraft Crashes In India; Was Operated By Myanmar To Ferry Its Soldiers - EurAsian Times
articles.description: A Myanmar military aircraft encountered a mishap during its landing at Lengpui Airport in Mizoram, India, on January 23. The incident, occurring at around 10:30 am local time, left at least eight of the 14 individuals on board injured.
